{"questionId":"22227655","questionHtml":"<p>Show that&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>10</mn></munderover><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>90</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>25</mn><mo> </mo><mi>ln</mi><mo> </mo><mn>3</mn></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>attempt to substitute first term and their common difference into <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>S</mi><mn>10</mn></msub></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mfenced><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>+</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo> </mo><mn>9</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo> </mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp; &nbsp;OR&nbsp; &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>10</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mfenced><mrow><mn>2</mn><mfenced><mrow><mn>9</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo> </mo><mi>ln</mi><mo> </mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>+</mo><mn>9</mn><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>-</mo><mi>ln</mi><mo> </mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;(or equivalent)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>5</mn><mfenced><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>18</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>5</mn><mo> </mo><mi>ln</mi><mo> </mo><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfenced></math>&nbsp;(or equivalent in terms of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>ln</mi><mo> </mo><mn>3</mn></math>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><munderover><mi>Σ</mi><mrow><mi>i</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mn>10</mn></munderover><msub><mi>u</mi><mi>i</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>90<